# Authentication Flow

## Objective
Implement user login and registration using Supabase Auth.

## Tasks
1. Create a Supabase client utility in SvelteKit.
2. Implement a login/signup view (`/login` route).
3. Wire up GitHub OAuth or Email Auth using `supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth`.
4. Ensure robust session hand-off on callback (`/auth/callback`).
